      <title>Anthropic 正在洽谈筹集 600 亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/anthropic-in-talks-for-funding-at-60-billion-value-wsj-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据两位知情人士透露，OpenAI 的竞争对手 Anthropic 正在进行深入谈判，将在新一轮融资中筹集 20 亿美元，这将使该初创公司的估值达到 600 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/anthropic-in-talks-for-funding-at-60-billion-value-wsj-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 18:28:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
